<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.4/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<div class="alert alert-warning alert-dismissible" role="alert">
  <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">
    <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
  </button>
  <p>We’re excited to announce that we’ll be starting the retirement process for Canvabadges the week of April 30th and migrating all existing users over to Badgr.</p>
  <p>Badgr is free to use and offers a number of compelling features including a built-in leaderboard. The Badgr Team will be offering a webinar on the transition as well as a transition guide. All existing Canvabadges will automatically appear in Badgr as part of the transition. Canvabadges will be shutdown, with access to non-migrated data unrecoverably lost, on December 31st 2018.</p>
  <p>Please contact your CSM if you have any questions about the transition.</p>
</div>

<h2><img src="<%= @org.settings['image'] || "/organizations/default.png" %>" alt=""/> Select a Badge to Embed</h2>
<p style="margin-top: -35px; padding-left: 95px;">Or create a new one. (<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I9ZJdh6_jLE#t=96" target="_blank">learn more</a>)</p>

<div class="row">
<div class="span10 offset1" style="padding-top: 15px;">
  <% @badge_configs.compact.each do |bc| %>
    <div class="badge_config select_badge_config" data-id="<%= bc.reuse_code %>" style="cursor: pointer;">
      <% settings = bc.settings || {} %>
      <a href="#"><img src='<%= settings['badge_url'] %>' style='float: left; margin-right: 10px;' class='thumbnail'/></a>
      <h2>
        <a href="#" class='name'><%= settings['badge_name'] || "Unnamed Badge" %></a>
      </h2>
      <p class='desc'><%= settings['badge_description'] %></p>

      <% if settings['hours'] %>
        <p>Approx hours: <%= settings['hours'] %></p>
      <% end %>
      <div style='clear: left;'></div>
    </div>
  <% end %>
  <% code = Digest::MD5.hexdigest(Time.now.to_i.to_s + rand.to_s) %>
  <div class="badge_config select_badge_config" data-proposed_id="list" style="cursor: pointer;">
    <img src='https://cdn3.iconfinder.com/data/icons/other-icons/48/list-128.png' style='float: left; margin-right: 10px; height: 50px; width: 50px; padding: 5px 24px' class='thumbnail'/>
    <h2>
    Badge List
    </h2>
    <p class='desc' style="max-height: none; margin-top: -20px; padding-bottom: 5px;">
      Insert a link to the listing of all badges for the current course.
    </p>
    <div style='clear: left;'></div>
  </div>
  <div class="badge_config" data-proposed_id="<%= code %>">
    <img src='data:image/png;base64,' style='float: left; margin-right: 10px;' class='thumbnail'/>
    <h2>
    Create a New Badge
    </h2>
    <p class='desc' style="max-height: none; margin-top: -20px; padding-bottom: 5px;">
      <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Badge Name" class="name"/>
      <button type="button" class="select_badge_config btn">Add Badge</button>
    </p>
    <div style='clear: left;'></div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
